# Maestro E2E test screenshots (generated at runtime)
.maestro/**/*.png
# Mock server PID file
.maestro/scripts/.mock-server.pid

# Generated native projects (CNG). `expo run:{android,ios}` produces these
# locally; leaving them tracked makes EAS Build upload them as-is and skip
# prebuild, which (a) shipped a stale iOS Expo.plist with OTA disabled (#5642)
# and (b) forces `eas update` into bare-workflow mode where the runtimeVersion
# policy is rejected. Both native dirs are now CNG: EAS regenerates them from
# app.json + config plugins each build. The LiveActivity widget (#2278) is
# regenerated by the `expo-live-activity` plugin (its `ios-files/` match the
# former committed Swift byte-for-byte), and the privacy manifest comes from
# `ios.privacyManifests` in app.json. Anchor with a leading slash so the rules
# match `packages/app/{android,ios}/` only, never a nested `**/{android,ios}/`.
/android/
/ios/
